public class CategoryValueDataSeriesItemImpl
extends Object
implements CategoryValueDataSeriesItem, ChildSelectable, SelectableShowableInLegend, Comparable<CategoryValueDataSeriesItemImpl>

A basic implementation of the CategoryValueDataSeriesItem interface. It can be used to represent a data item in a DataSeries. This implementation also implements the ChildSelectable interface which allows a SelectionChangedEvent.Handler to be set for it, the SelectableShowableInLegend interface which marks it as both selectable and showable in the Legend and the Comparable interface to define how one CategoryValueDataSeriesItemImpl is compared to another.
